    "html": "<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px; border: 3px solid #8a9aad; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); color: #2c3e50;\">\n  <!-- 顶部状态栏 -->\n  <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #4a6fa5, #6a8bc5); padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: #ecf0f1; font-weight: bold;\">\n    <div>📍 <span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\">客厅</span></div>\n    <div>🕒 第1天 上午</div>\n    <div>⚡ 精力: <span style=\"color: #2ecc71;\">85/100</span></div>\n    <div>💰 金钱: <span style=\"color: #f39c12;\">¥1,250</span></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- 中央区域 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <!-- 地点描述与交互 -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 3; background: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #7f8c8d; box-shadow: inset 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #34495e; border-bottom: 2px dashed #bdc3c7; padding-bottom: 8px;\">🏠 客厅</h3>\n      <div style=\"white-space: pre-line; line-height: 1.6; color: #2c3e50; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #dfe6e9; min-height: 180px;\">客厅宽敞明亮，落地窗外是一片绿意盎然的小花园。阳光透过玻璃洒在米白色的沙发上，形成温暖的光斑。茶几上放着一杯喝了一半的茶，还冒着若有若无的热气。电视柜旁的书架上摆满了各种书籍。空气中飘散着淡淡的檀香味，让人感到宁静舒适。\n\n你注意到：\n🔹 沙发扶手上搭着一条浅灰色的围巾\n🔹 茶几下面压着一张便签纸\n🔹 书架上的书籍似乎可以翻阅\n🔹 落地窗通往小花园</div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;\">\n        <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2980b9); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #1a5276; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: all 0.2s;\">📝 查看便签纸</button>\n        <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #2ecc71, #27ae60); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #1e8449; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: all 0.2s;\">🧣 检查围巾</button>\n        <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #9b59b6, #8e44ad); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #6c3483; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: all 0.2s;\">📚 翻阅书籍</button>\n        <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #e74c3c, #c0392b); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #922b21; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: all 0.2s;\">🌿 前往花园</button>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #7f8c8d; padding: 10px; background: #f1f2f6; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #bdc3c7;\">💡 提示：点击可交互物品触发事件，拖拽物品到角色头像可赠送礼物。</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 角色列表 -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #7f8c8d; box-shadow: inset 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #34495e; border-bottom: 2px dashed #bdc3c7; padding-bottom: 8px;\">👥 当前角色</h3>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #d5dbdb; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4); border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid #e74c3c; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px;\">👩</div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;\">林月</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f8c8d;\">📍 在房间</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #27ae60;\">❤️ 好感度: 65</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #d5dbdb; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb); border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid #3498db; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px;\">👨</div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;\">赵明</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f8c8d;\">📍 房间104</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #27ae60;\">❤️ 好感度: 45</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #d5dbdb; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2, #fcb69f); border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid #f39c12; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin-right: 15px;\">👧</div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50;\">小雅</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f8c8d;\">📍 图书馆</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #27ae60;\">❤️ 好感度: 70</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #e8f4fc; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #3498db; font-size: 0.85em; color: #2c3e50;\">💬 点击角色头像开始对话，或从背包拖拽物品赠送。</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- 底部导航 -->\n  <div style=\"background: #34495e; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #2c3e50; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; align-items: center;\">\n    <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #1abc9c, #16a085); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #0e6655; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: all 0.2s;\">🚶 移动</button>\n    <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #f39c12, #e67e22); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #b9770e; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: all 0.2s;\">📋 任务</button>\n    <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #9b59b6, #8e44ad); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #6c3483; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: all 0.2s;\">👤 角色</button>\n    <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2980b9); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #1a5276; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: all 0.2s;\">🎒 背包</button>\n    <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #95a5a6, #7f8c8d); color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #5d6d7e; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: all 0.2s;\">⚙️ 设置</button>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- 快捷状态提示 -->\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px; background: #fff8e1; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #fdd835; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; color: #5d4037;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 24px;\">📌</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当前线索</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;\">小雅留言提到赵明想约晚上去新咖啡馆。</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 0.85em; color: #8d6e63;\">🕒 时间推进会触发新事件</div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
