    "html": "<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf6e3 0%, #f5e6ca 100%); border: 3px solid #d4a574; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #5d4037; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin: 0; color: #8b4513; font-size: 28px; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.2);\">✨ 欢迎来到阳光公寓 ✨</h1>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #a0522d; margin-top: 8px;\">你刚刚搬进104室，开始了新的合租生活</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: rgba(255, 248, 225, 0.8); border: 2px dashed #d4a574; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: pre-line; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; font-size: 15px;\">在开始探索之前，请先告诉我一些关于你的基本信息，这样你的室友们也能更好地了解你。</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #fff8e1; border: 2px solid #ffb74d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color: #e65100; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffb74d; padding-bottom: 8px;\">📝 请设定你的角色</h3>\n        \n        <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;\">\n            <div style=\"background: white; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: #bf360c;\">1. 姓名</strong>\n                <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #5d4037;\">你希望被称呼为什么名字？</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px; background: #fff3e0; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ffcc80;\">等待输入...</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"background: white; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: #bf360c;\">2. 性别</strong>\n                <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #5d4037;\">男性 / 女性 / 其他</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px;\">\n                    <button style=\"flex: 1; padding: 6px; background: #ffecb3; border: 1px solid #ffb74d; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;\">♂️ 男性</button>\n                    <button style=\"flex: 1; padding: 6px; background: #ffecb3; border: 1px solid #ffb74d; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;\">♀️ 女性</button>\n                    <button style=\"flex: 1; padding: 6px; background: #ffecb3; border: 1px solid #ffb74d; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;\">🌈 其他</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"background: white; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: #bf360c;\">3. 年龄</strong>\n                <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #5d4037;\">建议20-35岁之间</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px; background: #fff3e0; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ffcc80;\">滑动选择: 20 ──●── 35</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"background: white; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: #bf360c;\">4. 工作</strong>\n                <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #5d4037;\">你目前从事什么职业？</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px; background: #fff3e0; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ffcc80;\">输入职业...</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div style=\"background: white; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px; grid-column: span 2;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: #bf360c;\">5. 爱好</strong>\n                <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #5d4037;\">你平时喜欢做什么？</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px; background: #fff3e0; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ffcc80; min-height: 60px;\">描述你的兴趣爱好...</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #e8f5e9; border: 2px solid #81c784; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: pre-line; margin: 0; color: #2e7d32; font-size: 14px;\">💡 <strong>系统提示：</strong>这些设定会影响后续对话选项和事件触发，请认真选择。</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 25px;\">\n        <button style=\"background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9800, #ff5722); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 25px; padding: 12px 40px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.3); transition: all 0.3s;\">🚀 完成创建，开始游戏</button>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 10px; color: #795548; font-size: 13px;\">设定完成后，你的角色卡将会更新，游戏将正式开始</p>\n    </div>\n</div>",
    "sections": []
  },
