style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #42a5f5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; text-align: center;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #0d47a1; margin-bottom: 5px;\">🎯</div>\n            <strong style=\"display: block; color: #1565c0;\">当前任务</strong>\n            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #424242; font-size: 14px;\">与小雅交谈</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #e1f5fe; border: 2px solid #29b6f6; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color: #0277bd; margin-top: 0; font-size: 16px;\">🔍 公寓关系网络</h3>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-around; align-items: center; margin-top: 10px;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: #bbdefb; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #42a5f5; margin: 0 auto 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">林</div>\n                <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px;\">林月</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #42a5f5;\">↔️</div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: #bbdefb; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #42a5f5; margin: 0 auto 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">赵</div>\n                <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px;\">赵明</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #42a5f5;\">↔️</div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: #bbdefb; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #42a5f5; margin: 0 auto 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">雅</div>\n                <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px;\">小雅</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #42a5f5;\">↔️</div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 50px; background: #ffecb3; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #ffb74d; margin: 0 auto 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">W</div>\n                <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px;\">Wion</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #f3e5f5; border: 2px solid #ba68c8; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color: #7b1fa2; margin-top: 0; font-size: 16px;\">📌 下一步指引</h3>\n        <p style=\"white-space: pre-line; margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #4a148c; font-size: 14px;\">角色创建已完成！你已解锁新角色“小雅”。\n• 与小雅交谈，了解公寓情况\n• 探索客厅环境\n• 查看便签纸上的信息\n• 准备晚上的咖啡馆之约</p>\n    </div>\n</div>",
